1
00:00:08,250 --> 00:00:09,500
- EARTH.

2
00:00:09,542 --> 00:00:11,250
FIRE.

3
00:00:11,291 --> 00:00:13,041
AIR.

4
00:00:13,083 --> 00:00:14,917
WATER.

5
00:00:14,959 --> 00:00:19,333
ONLY THE AVATAR
CAN MASTER ALL FOUR ELEMENTS

6
00:00:19,375 --> 00:00:21,208
AND BRING BALANCE
TO THE WORLD.

7
00:00:27,667 --> 00:00:30,041
- AMON'S REVOLUTION
GROWS STRONGER BY THE DAY.

8
00:00:30,083 --> 00:00:31,792
FIRST, HE ATTACKED
THE BENDING ARENA.

9
00:00:31,834 --> 00:00:33,041
THEN IT WAS DISCOVERED

10
00:00:33,083 --> 00:00:34,458
THAT HIROSHI SATO
WAS THE MASTERMIND

11
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:36,959
BEHIND THE EQUALIST GLOVES
AND MECHA-TANKS.

12
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:39,542
AND MOST RECENTLY, AMON AMBUSHED
COUNCILMAN TARRLOK,

13
00:00:39,583 --> 00:00:40,875
TOOK HIS BENDING,

14
00:00:40,917 --> 00:00:43,083
AND NEARLY CAPTURED
THE AVATAR AS WELL.

15
00:00:43,125 --> 00:00:46,333
EVERYONE IS ON EDGE WONDERING,
WHERE WILL AMON STRIKE NEXT?

16
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:54,709
[somber music]

17
00:00:54,750 --> 00:01:02,500
♪ ♪

18
00:01:22,291 --> 00:01:24,250
- DADDY, YOU'RE HOME.

19
00:01:24,291 --> 00:01:27,000
WE WAITED UP FOR YOU.
IS KORRA OKAY?

20
00:01:27,041 --> 00:01:29,875
- YES, SHE'S FINE,
SWEETIE.

21
00:01:29,917 --> 00:01:31,291
- I WAS SCARED.

22
00:01:31,333 --> 00:01:32,959
I THOUGHT SHE WASN'T
COMING BACK.

23
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,959
- I'M SORRY
YOU WERE SCARED,

24
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,166
BUT EVERYTHING IS GOING
TO BE FINE NOW.

25
00:01:37,208 --> 00:01:40,125
I PROMISE.

26
00:01:40,166 --> 00:01:43,959
- MMM.

27
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,583
MMM.

28
00:01:46,625 --> 00:01:49,166
THE FOOD TASTES
AMAZING, PEMA.

29
00:01:49,208 --> 00:01:51,000
I'M FINALLY STARTING
TO FEEL LIKE MYSELF AGAIN.

30
00:01:51,041 --> 00:01:54,875
- WE'RE SO THANKFUL
YOU'RE HOME SAFE.

31
00:01:54,917 --> 00:01:56,375
- LET ME HELP.

32
00:01:56,417 --> 00:01:57,834
- KORRA, I REALIZE
YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH A LOT,

33
00:01:57,875 --> 00:01:59,792
BUT I NEED TO KNOW
EVERYTHING THAT HAPPENED.

34
00:01:59,834 --> 00:02:04,959
- WELL, FIRST OFF,
TARRLOK ISN'T WHO HE SAYS HE IS.

35
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,208
HE'S YAKONE'S SON.

36
00:02:06,250 --> 00:02:09,041
- IT ALL
MAKES SENSE NOW.

37
00:02:09,083 --> 00:02:11,083
THAT'S HOW TARRLOK WAS ABLE
TO BLOODBEND US

38
00:02:11,125 --> 00:02:12,125
WITHOUT A FULL MOON.

39
00:02:12,166 --> 00:02:13,166
- BUT HOW DID YOU ESCAPE?

40
00:02:13,208 --> 00:02:14,834
AND WHERE'S TARRLOK?

41
00:02:14,875 --> 00:02:18,000
- AMON CAPTURED HIM
AND TOOK HIS BENDING.

42
00:02:18,041 --> 00:02:19,250
- WHAT?
- YEAH.

43
00:02:19,291 --> 00:02:21,333
HE SHOWED UP
OUT OF NOWHERE.

44
00:02:21,375 --> 00:02:22,417
HE ALMOST
GOT ME TOO.

45
00:02:22,458 --> 00:02:25,125
- THIS IS VERY
DISTURBING NEWS.

46
00:02:25,166 --> 00:02:27,125
AMON IS BECOMING
EMBOLDENED.

47
00:02:27,166 --> 00:02:30,542
TAKING OUT A COUNCILMAN,
ALMOST CAPTURING THE AVATAR--

48
00:02:30,583 --> 00:02:35,333
I FEAR AMON IS ENTERING
HIS END GAME.

49
00:02:37,709 --> 00:02:39,250
- [crying out]

50
00:02:39,291 --> 00:02:40,709
- PEMA,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

51
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:43,417
- THE BABY IS JUST KICKING
REALLY HARD, IS ALL.

52
00:02:43,458 --> 00:02:45,667
I'M FINE.
- SHOULD I GET TENZIN?

53
00:02:45,709 --> 00:02:48,375
- NO REASON TO WORRY HIM.
IT'S NOTHING.

54
00:02:48,417 --> 00:02:50,542
- CAN I GET
SOME HOT WATER?

55
00:02:50,583 --> 00:02:52,417
KORRA NEEDS
MORE TEA.

56
00:02:52,458 --> 00:02:54,333
- YOU'RE A FIREBENDER.
BOIL IT YOURSELF.

57
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:03,041
- I'M GONNA STEP OUT
IN CASE YOU TWO WANT TO TALK.

58
00:03:06,333 --> 00:03:08,291
- IS THERE SOMETHING
WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT?

59
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:12,083
- I'VE NOTICED
HOW YOU TREAT KORRA.

60
00:03:12,125 --> 00:03:14,291
HOW YOU ACTED
WHEN SHE WAS MISSING.

61
00:03:14,333 --> 00:03:15,500
YOU HAVE FEELINGS
FOR HER, DON'T YOU?

62
00:03:15,542 --> 00:03:17,542
- WHAT?
NO.

63
00:03:17,583 --> 00:03:19,917
SHE WAS TAKEN
BY A CRAZY BLOODBENDER.

64
00:03:19,959 --> 00:03:21,000
HOW DID YOU
EXPECT ME TO ACT?

65
00:03:21,041 --> 00:03:23,083
- I LIKE KORRA.

66
00:03:23,125 --> 00:03:24,625
BUT YOU'VE BEEN KEEPING
THE TRUTH FROM ME

67
00:03:24,667 --> 00:03:25,750
THIS WHOLE TIME.

68
00:03:25,792 --> 00:03:28,375
- THE TRUTH?
ABOUT WHAT?

69
00:03:28,417 --> 00:03:30,083
- YOU'RE REALLY
GONNA MAKE ME SAY IT?

70
00:03:30,125 --> 00:03:32,458
- YES, BECAUSE I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

71
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:33,750
- THE KISS, MAKO.

72
00:03:33,792 --> 00:03:34,917
I KNOW.

73
00:03:34,959 --> 00:03:39,000
- I--WELL...

74
00:03:39,041 --> 00:03:40,750
BOLIN TOLD YOU,
DIDN'T HE?

75
00:03:40,792 --> 00:03:42,917
- DON'T BLAME YOUR BROTHER
FOR WHAT YOU DID.

76
00:03:42,959 --> 00:03:44,959
DO YOU HAVE FEELINGS
FOR KORRA OR NOT?

77
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,709
- LOOK, THINGS ARE CRAZY
RIGHT NOW.

78
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:49,875
CAN WE DEAL WITH
OUR RELATIONSHIP PROBLEMS LATER?

79
00:03:49,917 --> 00:03:51,250
- WELL, THERE MIGHT NOT
BE ANY RELATIONSHIP

80
00:03:51,291 --> 00:03:52,792
TO WORRY ABOUT LATER.

81
00:03:52,834 --> 00:03:54,250
- ASAMI.

82
00:03:54,291 --> 00:03:56,583
[sighs]

83
00:03:56,625 --> 00:04:00,375
- LIN, UM, I-I NEED
TO ASK YOU A FAVOR.

84
00:04:00,417 --> 00:04:02,667
IT WOULD MEAN
THE WORLD TO ME,

85
00:04:02,709 --> 00:04:06,417
BUT I-I KNOW IT COULD BE
A POTENTIALLY AWKWARD SITUATION.

86
00:04:06,458 --> 00:04:08,458
FURTHERMORE--
- SPIT IT OUT ALREADY.

87
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:10,417
- WILL YOU STAY HERE AND WATCH
OVER PEMA AND THE CHILDREN

88
00:04:10,458 --> 00:04:12,125
WHILE I MEET
WITH THE COUNCIL?

89
00:04:12,166 --> 00:04:14,041
WITH EVERYTHING
THAT'S HAPPENED LATELY,

90
00:04:14,083 --> 00:04:16,583
I WANT TO BE SURE
MY FAMILY IS IN SAFE HANDS.

91
00:04:16,625 --> 00:04:20,375
- OF COURSE I'LL HELP,
OLD FRIEND.

92
00:04:20,417 --> 00:04:22,250
- I DIDN'T REALIZE
YOU TWO WERE OUT HERE.

93
00:04:22,291 --> 00:04:24,667
- PEMA!
UH, YES, YES.

94
00:04:24,709 --> 00:04:26,500
LIN HAS AGREED
TO HELP OUT AROUND HERE

95
00:04:26,542 --> 00:04:27,917
AND KEEP AN EYE ON THINGS
WHILE I'M AWAY.

96
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,417
- THANK YOU.

97
00:04:29,458 --> 00:04:30,917
I COULD USE
THE EXTRA PAIR OF HANDS.

98
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,083
- [giggling]

99
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:33,291
- WOULD YOU MIND
GIVING HIM A BATH?

100
00:04:33,333 --> 00:04:36,333
HE'S FILTHY.
- [laughing]

101
00:04:36,375 --> 00:04:38,583
- THIS IS NOT
WHAT I SIGNED ON FOR.

102
00:04:38,625 --> 00:04:39,875
- THANK YOU, LIN.

103
00:04:39,917 --> 00:04:43,917
OOGI, YIP, YIP.
[Oogi growling]

104
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:48,959
- I GOT TO POO.
REALLY BAD.

105
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,542
OOH! AH!

106
00:04:50,583 --> 00:04:52,458
UGH!

107
00:04:58,333 --> 00:04:59,917
- DO YOU KNOW
WHERE MY KEYS ARE?

108
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,709
I CAN'T FIND
THEM ANYWHERE.

109
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:03,500
- NO, DEAR.

110
00:05:03,542 --> 00:05:05,667
- OH, FOUND THEM.
- GOOD, DEAR.

111
00:05:05,709 --> 00:05:07,291
- DON'T WAIT UP FOR ME.

112
00:05:07,333 --> 00:05:09,917
THIS COUNCIL SESSION WILL
PROBABLY GO LATE INTO THE NIGHT.

113
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:10,959
[knocking]

114
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,917
- THE DOOR, DEAR.

115
00:05:15,792 --> 00:05:18,333
- WE'RE HERE TO FIX
A SPIDER-RAT PROBLEM.

116
00:05:18,375 --> 00:05:20,000
- I DIDN'T CALL
AN EXTERMINATOR.

117
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:25,458
- DEAR?

118
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:29,792
[growling]

119
00:05:48,667 --> 00:05:50,291
- [grunts]

120
00:05:59,417 --> 00:06:00,417
- UGH!

121
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,625
- AAH!
- OOF!

122
00:06:07,333 --> 00:06:09,959
- AAH!

123
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,959
OH, I'M SO RELIEVED
TO SEE YOU.

124
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,083
- THE OTHER COUNCIL MEMBERS,
ARE THEY ALL RIGHT?

125
00:06:14,125 --> 00:06:15,542
- I'M AFRAID NOT.

126
00:06:15,583 --> 00:06:17,750
I JUST RECEIVED A CALL
FROM CHIEF SAIKHAN.

127
00:06:17,792 --> 00:06:19,750
THEY'VE ALL
BEEN CAPTURED.

128
00:06:19,792 --> 00:06:21,250
- THIS CAN'T BE HAPPENING.

129
00:06:21,291 --> 00:06:23,250
- THE LEADERSHIP
OF REPUBLIC CITY

130
00:06:23,291 --> 00:06:26,333
IS IN YOUR HANDS NOW.

131
00:06:26,375 --> 00:06:28,208
[explosion]

132
00:06:34,792 --> 00:06:38,000
[dramatic music]

133
00:06:38,041 --> 00:06:40,625
IT IS A TRAGIC
DAY INDEED!

134
00:06:45,375 --> 00:06:47,000
- ALL RIGHT, KIDS.
TIME TO GO INSIDE.

135
00:06:49,458 --> 00:06:51,166
- WE HEARD EXPLOSIONS.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

136
00:06:51,208 --> 00:06:53,166
- REPUBLIC CITY
IS UNDER ATTACK.

137
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:08,834
- I'VE DREAMED OF THIS DAY
FOR SO LONG.

138
00:07:08,875 --> 00:07:10,083
- YES.

139
00:07:10,125 --> 00:07:12,125
THE TIME HAS COME
FOR THE EQUALISTS

140
00:07:12,166 --> 00:07:15,959
TO CLAIM REPUBLIC CITY
AS THEIR OWN.

141
00:07:26,083 --> 00:07:28,291
[sirens blaring]

142
00:07:32,083 --> 00:07:33,792
- WHERE DID YOU SAY
YOU PARKED THE CAR?

143
00:07:33,834 --> 00:07:36,375
- IT'S RIGHT
AROUND HERE SOMEWHERE.

144
00:07:36,417 --> 00:07:40,917
THERE IT IS.

145
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:43,291
- WOW, NICE PARKING JOB.

146
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:46,917
- HEY, YOU GUYS GOT ARRESTED
AND LEFT ME ALONE WITH THE CAR.

147
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:49,542
I MADE IT VERY CLEAR
I DON'T KNOW HOW TO DRIVE.

148
00:07:49,583 --> 00:07:52,583
- ALL THINGS CONSIDERED,
YOU DID A GREAT JOB.

149
00:07:52,625 --> 00:07:56,291
BUT HOW ARE WE GONNA PAY
FOR ALL THESE PARKING TICKETS?

150
00:07:56,333 --> 00:07:58,166
[gasps]

151
00:07:58,208 --> 00:08:00,208
- RELAX, THE CITY'S
UNDER ATTACK.

152
00:08:00,250 --> 00:08:02,291
THE POLICE HAVE MORE IMPORTANT
THINGS TO WORRY ABOUT.

153
00:08:05,166 --> 00:08:07,208
- THIS'LL COME IN HANDY.

154
00:08:10,375 --> 00:08:14,250
WHY DON'T YOU SIT IN BACK
WITH KORRA?

155
00:08:14,291 --> 00:08:17,500
- I THINK I WILL.

156
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:23,667
- EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT?
- YEAH.

157
00:08:23,709 --> 00:08:24,709
EVERYTHING'S TERRIFIC.

158
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:25,709
[tires screeching]

159
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:28,875
- CAR!
OH, WE'RE GOOD.

160
00:08:28,917 --> 00:08:32,792
[sirens blaring]

161
00:08:32,834 --> 00:08:35,083
- CHIEF, AIR UNIT SEVEN
WAS JUST TAKEN OUT

162
00:08:35,125 --> 00:08:36,542
BY AN EQUALIST AIRSHIP.

163
00:08:36,583 --> 00:08:37,959
THEY'VE CRASHED
INTO THE HARBOR.

164
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,458
- SEND A RIVER
RESCUE UNIT.

165
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:42,709
- CHIEF, ALL RIVER RESCUE SHIPS
HAVE BEEN SABOTAGED.

166
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:43,959
- WHAT?

167
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,542
- CHIEF SAIKHAN.

168
00:08:45,583 --> 00:08:47,583
- TENZIN, AM I GLAD
TO SEE YOU.

169
00:08:47,625 --> 00:08:49,458
I WAS AFRAID
YOU'D BEEN CAPTURED TOO.

170
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,750
- I'M THE ONLY
COUNCIL MEMBER LEFT.

171
00:08:50,792 --> 00:08:52,083
WHAT'S THE STATUS?

172
00:08:52,125 --> 00:08:53,959
- AMON HAS LAUNCHED
SIMULTANEOUS ATTACKS

173
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,291
ACROSS THE BOROUGHS.

174
00:08:55,333 --> 00:08:56,458
THE POLICE ARE TRYING
TO REGAIN CONTROL,

175
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:59,625
BUT WE'RE SPREAD
TOO THIN.

176
00:08:59,667 --> 00:09:02,542
- I NEED TO SEND A WIRE.
- TO WHOM, COUNCILMAN?

177
00:09:02,583 --> 00:09:04,500
- THE GENERAL
OF THE UNITED FORCES.

178
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:14,417
[coughing]

179
00:09:14,458 --> 00:09:17,250
- COUNCILMAN, YOUR WIRE
HAS BEEN SENT.

180
00:09:17,291 --> 00:09:18,792
- CHIEF, THE PHONE LINES
JUST WENT DEAD.

181
00:09:18,834 --> 00:09:21,542
[alarm sounding]

182
00:09:21,583 --> 00:09:26,458
[alarm dying out]
- [gasps]

183
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,291
- CATCH.

184
00:09:31,458 --> 00:09:33,333
- SAIKHAN,
THE VENTS!

185
00:09:35,041 --> 00:09:38,875
[coughing]

186
00:09:38,917 --> 00:09:40,667
WE NEED
TO EVACUATE IMMEDIATELY.

187
00:09:40,709 --> 00:09:43,333
EVERYONE STAY
CLOSE TO ME.

188
00:09:55,792 --> 00:09:58,417
[all gasp]

189
00:09:58,458 --> 00:10:00,917
NOT THESE
MECHA-TANKS AGAIN.

190
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:04,959
- AAH!
- AAH!

191
00:10:05,041 --> 00:10:07,250
- OOF!
- UGH!

192
00:10:08,667 --> 00:10:11,834
- [grunting]

193
00:10:11,875 --> 00:10:14,625
AAH!

194
00:10:14,667 --> 00:10:16,500
[straining]

195
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:39,792
- [grunting]

196
00:10:39,834 --> 00:10:41,667
[groans]

197
00:10:41,709 --> 00:10:44,542
SAIKHAN, NO.

198
00:10:54,041 --> 00:10:55,291
[all groaning]

199
00:10:55,333 --> 00:11:00,291
[groans]

200
00:11:11,458 --> 00:11:13,208
- JUMP!

201
00:11:24,709 --> 00:11:27,417
- UGH!

202
00:11:27,458 --> 00:11:29,375
AAH!

203
00:11:48,417 --> 00:11:50,333
- [grunts]

204
00:11:55,375 --> 00:11:57,709
- AAH!

205
00:12:02,041 --> 00:12:04,417
- UGH!

206
00:12:04,458 --> 00:12:06,500
- AAH!

207
00:12:06,542 --> 00:12:09,792
- OH!

208
00:12:09,834 --> 00:12:11,959
[fighting cry]

209
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,250
- [groans]
THANK YOU.

210
00:12:29,291 --> 00:12:31,917
- TENZIN HAS ESCAPED
ONCE AGAIN.

211
00:12:31,959 --> 00:12:33,875
I CAN'T STAND
TO SEE ASAMI FIGHTING

212
00:12:33,917 --> 00:12:36,125
ALONGSIDE THOSE BENDERS.

213
00:12:36,166 --> 00:12:38,667
- WE WILL CAPTURE THEM
BEFORE LONG,

214
00:12:38,709 --> 00:12:40,417
AND YOU WILL HAVE
YOUR DAUGHTER BACK.

215
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,333
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

216
00:12:44,375 --> 00:12:46,583
- I'M FINE.
THANK YOU, KIDS.

217
00:12:46,625 --> 00:12:47,792
ANOTHER MOMENT LATER,

218
00:12:47,834 --> 00:12:49,667
AND I WOULD'VE BEEN
ON MY WAY TO AMON.

219
00:12:49,709 --> 00:12:52,125
- UH, GUYS, LOOK.

220
00:12:54,375 --> 00:12:55,291
- OH, NO.

221
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:33,250
- EVERYONE, HIDE INSIDE
AND REMAIN CALM.

222
00:13:33,291 --> 00:13:34,959
- AAH!

223
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,250
- PULL IT
TOGETHER, PEMA.

224
00:13:36,291 --> 00:13:37,333
DIDN'T I JUST SAY,
"REMAIN CALM"?

225
00:13:37,375 --> 00:13:39,208
- MOMMY, WHAT'S WRONG?

226
00:13:39,250 --> 00:13:42,208
- THE BABY'S COMING!

227
00:13:42,250 --> 00:13:43,709
- OH, NO.

228
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,000
- NOT NOW, BABY!

229
00:13:45,041 --> 00:13:48,291
- [moaning]

230
00:13:56,709 --> 00:13:59,750
[dramatic music]

231
00:13:59,792 --> 00:14:07,458
♪ ♪

232
00:14:31,709 --> 00:14:35,250
[grunting]

233
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:43,917
[grunting]

234
00:14:48,208 --> 00:14:49,750
- THE CHILDREN,
WHERE ARE THEY?

235
00:14:49,792 --> 00:14:51,208
- DON'T WORRY.

236
00:14:51,250 --> 00:14:52,792
THEY'RE IN THE OTHER ROOM,
TOTALLY SAFE.

237
00:14:56,875 --> 00:14:58,083
- AAH!

238
00:14:58,125 --> 00:15:02,792
[groans]

239
00:15:02,834 --> 00:15:05,458
- STAY AWAY FROM MY DAD'S
EX-GIRLFRIEND.

240
00:15:07,875 --> 00:15:09,792
- UGH! OOF!

241
00:15:09,834 --> 00:15:11,375
- JINORA!

242
00:15:11,417 --> 00:15:12,834
YOU SHOULDN'T
BE OUT HERE!

243
00:15:12,875 --> 00:15:14,625
[grunting]

244
00:15:14,667 --> 00:15:16,583
- GET OFF OUR ISLAND!

245
00:15:16,625 --> 00:15:19,000
[grunting]

246
00:15:19,041 --> 00:15:22,417
- GIRLS, YOU NEED TO GO
BACK INSIDE THIS INSTANT.

247
00:15:22,458 --> 00:15:25,583
- TASTE MY FURY!

248
00:15:25,625 --> 00:15:28,542
[farts]

249
00:15:28,583 --> 00:15:29,834
- MEELO, BE CAREFUL!

250
00:15:29,875 --> 00:15:31,792
- [fighting grunts]

251
00:15:31,834 --> 00:15:35,166
[farts]

252
00:15:35,208 --> 00:15:38,834
[roaring]

253
00:15:38,875 --> 00:15:42,917
- NEVER MIND.

254
00:15:42,959 --> 00:15:44,500
TAKE THESE EQUALISTS
AND LOCK THEM

255
00:15:44,542 --> 00:15:47,208
IN THE TEMPLE'S BASEMENT.
NICE WORK, KIDS.

256
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:48,208
[growling]

257
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:49,667
- DAD!

258
00:15:49,709 --> 00:15:52,834
[growling]

259
00:15:52,875 --> 00:15:55,417
- OH, THANK GOODNESS
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

260
00:15:55,458 --> 00:15:58,000
- WE CAUGHT
THE BAD GUYS.

261
00:15:58,041 --> 00:15:59,542
- YOU LET THEM FIGHT?

262
00:15:59,583 --> 00:16:01,333
DO YOU REALIZE
WHAT COULD'VE HAPPENED?

263
00:16:01,375 --> 00:16:04,041
- I WOULD'VE BEEN TOAST
IF IT WEREN'T FOR YOUR KIDS.

264
00:16:04,083 --> 00:16:05,083
YOU SHOULD BE PROUD.

265
00:16:05,125 --> 00:16:08,500
YOU TAUGHT THEM WELL.

266
00:16:10,291 --> 00:16:14,291
GO ON.
BE WITH YOUR WIFE.

267
00:16:14,333 --> 00:16:17,625
[baby wailing]

268
00:16:17,667 --> 00:16:22,000
- PEMA!

269
00:16:22,041 --> 00:16:23,875
[baby cries]

270
00:16:23,917 --> 00:16:27,417
- TENZIN.

271
00:16:27,458 --> 00:16:28,709
- I'M HERE, PEMA.

272
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:31,792
- OUR NEW SON.

273
00:16:31,834 --> 00:16:36,041
- [cooing]

274
00:16:36,083 --> 00:16:38,041
- HELLO.

275
00:16:39,917 --> 00:16:42,291
COME, MEET
YOUR NEW BROTHER.

276
00:16:42,333 --> 00:16:45,125
- A BROTHER?
WELL, IT'S ABOUT TIME.

277
00:16:45,166 --> 00:16:47,959
- WELCOME.

278
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:50,625
I'M IKKI, AND THIS IS JINORA
AND MEELO.

279
00:16:50,667 --> 00:16:52,500
WE HAVE A SUPER
GREAT FAMILY,

280
00:16:52,542 --> 00:16:55,083
AND WE'RE SO HAPPY
THAT YOU'RE A PART OF IT.

281
00:16:55,125 --> 00:16:56,834
- WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA NAME HIM?

282
00:16:56,875 --> 00:16:58,083
CAN I PICK?

283
00:16:58,125 --> 00:17:01,166
- WE ALREADY CHOSE
A NAME.

284
00:17:01,208 --> 00:17:02,417
- ROHAN.

285
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:12,000
- I'M SO SORRY
TO INTERRUPT, BUT...

286
00:17:12,041 --> 00:17:13,792
MORE AIRSHIPS
ARE COMING.

287
00:17:13,834 --> 00:17:16,834
- EVERYTHING'S NOT
GONNA BE FINE,

288
00:17:16,875 --> 00:17:20,166
IS IT, DADDY?

289
00:17:20,208 --> 00:17:24,000
- [whimpering]

290
00:17:33,750 --> 00:17:35,834
- WHAT DO YOU WANT
TO DO, TENZIN?

291
00:17:35,875 --> 00:17:37,166
- [sighs]

292
00:17:37,208 --> 00:17:39,166
I NEED TO PROTECT
MY FAMILY

293
00:17:39,208 --> 00:17:42,000
AND GET THEM AS FAR AWAY
FROM THIS CONFLICT AS POSSIBLE.

294
00:17:42,041 --> 00:17:44,959
IF AMON GOT HIS HANDS
ON MY CHILDREN--

295
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,542
I HATE TO EVEN
THINK OF IT.

296
00:17:46,583 --> 00:17:48,417
- IF YOU'RE LEAVING,
THEN I'M GOING WITH YOU.

297
00:17:48,458 --> 00:17:49,750
- BUT--
- NO ARGUMENTS.

298
00:17:49,792 --> 00:17:52,417
YOU AND YOUR FAMILY
ARE THE LAST AIRBENDERS.

299
00:17:52,458 --> 00:17:53,583
THERE'S NO WAY
IN THE WORLD

300
00:17:53,625 --> 00:17:55,291
I'M LETTING AMON
TAKE YOUR BENDING AWAY.

301
00:17:55,333 --> 00:17:57,125
- THANK YOU, LIN.

302
00:17:57,166 --> 00:17:59,458
KORRA, I WANT YOU
TO LEAVE THIS ISLAND

303
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:01,333
AND HIDE
FOR THE TIME BEING.

304
00:18:01,375 --> 00:18:04,542
- I'M NOT GIVING UP.
- I'M NOT ASKING YOU TO.

305
00:18:04,583 --> 00:18:06,083
I'VE SENT WORD
TO THE UNITED FORCES.

306
00:18:06,125 --> 00:18:07,625
THEY WILL BE HERE SOON.

307
00:18:07,667 --> 00:18:10,625
AND ONCE MY FAMILY IS SAFE,
I WILL RETURN.

308
00:18:10,667 --> 00:18:13,792
WITH THE REINFORCEMENTS, WE CAN
TURN THE TIDE IN THIS WAR.

309
00:18:13,834 --> 00:18:18,458
- WHAT YOU'RE SAYING IS
WE NEED TO BE PATIENT.

310
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:20,500
- YOU'RE LEARNING WELL.

311
00:18:28,291 --> 00:18:30,625
STAY SAFE, KORRA.
- YOU TOO.

312
00:18:30,667 --> 00:18:32,709
- TENZIN, IF WE'RE LEAVING,
WE'D BETTER DO IT NOW.

313
00:18:36,083 --> 00:18:39,208
- OOGI, YIP, YIP.
[Oogi growling]

314
00:18:49,458 --> 00:18:52,208
[growls]

315
00:18:54,250 --> 00:18:57,208
[dramatic music]

316
00:18:57,250 --> 00:19:05,250
♪ ♪

317
00:19:08,417 --> 00:19:11,917
- GO.
WE'LL HOLD THEM OFF.

318
00:19:11,959 --> 00:19:15,041
- EVERYONE, CLIMB ON.

319
00:19:15,083 --> 00:19:17,250
LET'S GO, GIRL.

320
00:19:30,792 --> 00:19:34,375
- MOUSTACHE GUY!

321
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:37,750
[growling]

322
00:19:37,792 --> 00:19:42,333
- AAH!

323
00:19:42,375 --> 00:19:43,333
- NICE ONE, NAGA.

324
00:19:57,083 --> 00:20:01,125
[growls]

325
00:20:04,417 --> 00:20:05,458
- THEY'RE GAINING
ON US!

326
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:08,417
- FASTER, OOGI!
[Oogi growls]

327
00:20:23,959 --> 00:20:27,208
- WHATEVER HAPPENS TO ME,
DON'T TURN BACK.

328
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:30,458
- LIN, WHAT
ARE YOU DOING?

329
00:21:05,083 --> 00:21:09,417
- [grunts]

330
00:21:09,458 --> 00:21:12,333
OOF!

331
00:21:17,583 --> 00:21:19,291
UGH! AAH!

332
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:35,417
- THAT LADY
IS MY HERO.

333
00:21:35,458 --> 00:21:37,834
- YES, SHE IS.

334
00:21:37,875 --> 00:21:40,333
[growling]

335
00:21:44,667 --> 00:21:49,625
[growls]

336
00:21:49,667 --> 00:21:52,291
- KORRA,
WE SHOULD GET MOVING.

337
00:22:09,083 --> 00:22:13,458
- UGH!

338
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,417
- TELL ME WHERE
THE AVATAR IS,

339
00:22:15,458 --> 00:22:17,250
AND I'LL LET YOU
KEEP YOUR BENDING.

340
00:22:17,291 --> 00:22:20,792
- I WON'T TELL YOU ANYTHING,
YOU MONSTER.

341
00:22:20,834 --> 00:22:22,458
- VERY WELL.

342
00:22:31,375 --> 00:22:34,333
[somber music]

343
00:22:34,375 --> 00:22:37,542
♪ ♪

344
00:22:40,792 --> 00:22:43,291
- GENERAL, I JUST RECEIVED
A WIRE FROM THE AVATAR.

345
00:22:43,333 --> 00:22:46,917
SHE SAYS AMON AND HIS FORCES
HAVE GAINED CONTROL OF THE CITY.

346
00:22:46,959 --> 00:22:50,375
HOW DO YOU WANT
TO RESPOND?

347
00:22:50,417 --> 00:22:52,750
- TELL HER WE WILL BE ARRIVING
IN THREE DAYS TIME

348
00:22:52,792 --> 00:22:54,917
AND THAT I LOOK FORWARD
TO WINNING BACK REPUBLIC CITY.

349
00:22:54,959 --> 00:22:56,250
TOGETHER.

350
00:22:56,291 --> 00:22:58,250
- AS YOU WISH,
GENERAL IROH.
